AudioData.Text: Welcome to the demo scene for the track and measure add-on for VR Builder. Teleport to a station to check out some of the add-on's features.
AudioData.Key: Welcome to the demo scene for the track and measure add-on for VR Builder. Teleport to a station to check out some of the add-on's features.

AudioData.Text: Build a pyramid with the cubes. The timer will start when you grab the first cube. You can reset the table at any time by pressing that inconspicuous red button.
AudioData.Key: Build a pyramid with the cubes. The timer will start when you grab the first cube. You can reset the table at any time by pressing that inconspicuous red button.

AudioData.Text: It was a good performance, but you can do better.
AudioData.Key: It was a good performance, but you can do better.

AudioData.Text: You sure took your time! Next time, try to bring out your inner toddler.
AudioData.Key: You sure took your time! Next time, try to bring out your inner toddler.

AudioData.Text: You can reset the table to try again.
AudioData.Key: You can reset the table to try again.

AudioData.Text: Congratulations! You managed to trigger the line for the longest time threshold. You did this on purpose, right?
AudioData.Key: Congratulations! You managed to trigger the line for the longest time threshold. You did this on purpose, right?

AudioData.Text: That wasn't too hard, was it?
AudioData.Key: That wasn't too hard, was it?

AudioData.Text: Acting randomly would have yielded a better score. Did you deliberately choose to fail?
AudioData.Key: Acting randomly would have yielded a better score. Did you deliberately choose to fail?

AudioData.Text: You can do better. Why not try again?
AudioData.Key: You can do better. Why not try again?

AudioData.Text: Push the button corresponding to the color of the cube.
AudioData.Key: Push the button corresponding to the color of the cube.

AudioData.Text: Not to hurt your feelings, but are you sure you got the instructions right?
